---
title: Checkbox field
---
The `checkbox` field is used to store a `boolean`.

A single checkbox is used in the Admin UI for this field.

## Example usage

```typescript
draft: fields.checkbox({
  label: 'Draft',
  description: 'Set this post as draft to prevent it from being published'
})
```

## Type signature

```typescript
checkbox({
  label: string;
  defaultValue?: boolean;
  description?: string;
})
```
